title: Beautiful and Spacious Studio Apartment w/Large Balcony
posting_body: ['KNOLLWOOD TOWERS WEST', 'Welcome to Knollwood Towers West Apartments in Hopkins, Minnesota!', 'Knollwood Towers West offers studio, one bedroom or two bedroom units in this 7 story building.', 'Enjoy the new fitness center and underground parking.', 'Every apartment has a generously sized balcony with an east, west, north or south view.', 'Located off the main road and adjacent to Oakes Park with play structures for children, tennis courts and ball fields.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 510 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Cable Ready', '- Air Conditioner', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Dishwasher', '- Refrigerator', 'Community Amenities', '- Fitness Center', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '- Short Walk to Metro Transit Bus Line', '- Elevator', '- Community Room', '- Laundry Facilities', 'Pet Policy', 'NO PETS', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 MONTHLY RENT', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Knollwood Towers West', '1010 Lake St. Ne, Hopkins, MN, 55343', 'ehy2XBOiOd']
